# USDCHF H4 Bollinger Band Research Summary

## Research Objective

This phase of the project tested whether **volatility expansion (Bollinger Bands)** can identify reliable mean-reversion opportunities on USDCHF and how those results compare to the RSI chapter.

All studies used:

* USDCHF
* H4 Timeframe
* Bollinger Bands (20,2)

---

